"<h2>Tabs with icons<span class="status approved">Approved</span></h2>

<p>Wrapper element for tabs and content should contain <code>data-tabs</code> atribute with uniq value. So it is possible to have more than one tabs&amp;content elements on page.<br>Tabs can be used with any content of your choice.<br><code>data-section</code> attribute on tab and content div should match.<br>You can also use different icons for tabs. The styles are tailored for 4 or less tabs.</p>
<p>There is no styling for content inside. For a search mask example with responsive behavior for content see <a href="https://scout24.github.io/showcar-ui/#search-mask-target">here</a></p>
